com.autonomy.aci.client.annotations

Annotation Type IdolBuilderBuild


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface IdolBuilderBuild
    Designates the target method as the build method for a given IdolBuilder.

    This annotation has no effect if its parent class is not annotated with IdolBuilder.

    The target method must take no arguments and return an object whose type is the same as the enclosing class.
